  "texts": [
    "This significant increase in the identification of new material names can be attributed to GPT-3.5's inclination towards detailed extraction of composition and types while extracting material names (see Table S3).",
    "It is important to mention that variations in naming and co-referents of polymers were considered correct during the calculation of the F 1 score.",
    "Consequently, although there is a low overlap of the names exactly extracted by the methods as depicted in Fig. 4d, a high F 1 score is still maintained.",
    "For comparison, similar Venn diagrams for Tg and bandgap data extracted from the 630 abstracts are shown in Fig.",
    "Upon further investigation, we found that MaterialsBERT in some cases faced challenges in correctly associating property and material names in texts filled with numerous numbers and values."
